data.title: Scientific Reports
data.text:
Thank you to our July 2024 reviewers

High quality peer review sits at the heart of our editorial process, and we are deeply grateful to those researchers who give their time and effort to review on behalf of Scientific Reports.

Their expert guidance and insightful comments enable us to maintain our commitment to publishing scientifically robust, original research for the benefit of the entire scientific community.

To show our appreciation, we are delighted to bring you the names of those who reviewed for us last month.
